Installation Requirements:

GLIB

openssl:
https://www.openssl.org/source/
1. Download 2022-Mar-15 15:24:36 	openssl-1.1.1n.tar.gz
   and/or install `sudo apt install openssl libssl-dev`
2. Extract the file by running `sudo tar -xf openssl-1.1.1n.tar.gz -C /usr/include`
3. Navigate to `/usr/include/openssl-1.1.1n` and run `sudo ./config`
4. Run `sudo make install` and wait 3-5 minutes.